{"tid":1498252,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實罷工罷一兩日係無用","createTime":"2019-08-23T10:27:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T15:53:23.000Z","uid":103960,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"928601709f7fda333b2214b969140cc1b3508d1d","tid":1498252,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:27:53.000Z","msg":"罷得一兩日根本不痛不癢<br />\n就算有損失都未令到班友覺得擊中要害<br />\n係要無限期罷工呀<br />\n<br />\n航空業嘅各位：<br />\n今日國泰可以咁撚樣清洗員工<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">他朝其他航空公司都可以</span></span><br />\n要癱瘓機場就靠你地架啦！！<br />\n<br />\n其他人：<br />\n之前又話唔割國泰<br />\n依家國泰員工面<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">臨嚴重政治逼害</span></span><br />\n只有癱瘓成個香港<br />\n先可以幫到佢地！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">一齊無限期罷工啦！</span></span>"},{"pid":"8578db79f5e0aba3300d0fe8ce35210019f2c8cd","tid":1498252,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:28:05.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1286b08d8d8f07b6c2897b8ae117477846183cc2","tid":1498252,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:28:16.000Z","msg":"自推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10e1b2f73c8655730996e10fe96f5ca58d2b41c2","tid":1498252,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:28:35.000Z","msg":"大家係時候要組織一次真正嘅大罷工啦"},{"pid":"641099feaf462be9749269b08b7d857f0127e877","tid":1498252,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:28:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"49a212d9dbd220bcfddd6455c0963c872788e978","tid":1498252,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T10:28:56.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e4a1f10572d7fb124ff097c9faf77e9d150afe7","tid":1498252,"uid":103960,"like":0,"